        "installation": "<p>This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>In your WordPress admin panel, go to Plugins &gt; New Plugin, search for WP eCards and click &#8220;Install now&#8221;<\/li>\n<li>Alternatively, download the plugin and upload the contents of wp-ecards.zip to your plugins directory, which usually is \/wp-content\/plugins\/.<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin<\/li>\n<li>Authenticate the plugin with EcardWidget.com<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
